<p><strong>Large dragon, chaotic good</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 17 (natural armor)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 119 (14d10+42)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 40 ft., climb 40 ft., fly 80 ft.</p>

